strict matching (`getMatchingCoordinatesStrict`) while keeping the same output format.\\\\n\\\\n### Generating dependency graphs\\\\n\\\\nTo print deps.dev dependency graphs for resolved GAV coordinates while honoring the same `-Pcoordinates` filter semantics used by the harness:\\\\n\\\\n```console\\\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=all\\\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=group:artifact\\\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=group:artifact:version\\\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=1/16\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n[173 more lines in file. Use offset=121 to continue.]\\\"}], \\\"isError\\\": false, \\\"timestamp\\\": 1777415059982}}\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/logs/fused/org.scala-lang:scala3-interfaces:3.3.1/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-28T22-25-48-207454Z.log:498:[recv] {\\\"type\\\": \\\"turn_end\\\", \\\"message\\\": {\\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\", \\\"content\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"thinking\\\", \\\"thinking\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"thinkingSignature\\\": \\\"{\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"rs_0ffec6755bd7d4050169f133932788819090ab18f5c8153edf\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"reasoning\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"encrypted_content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"gAAAAABp8TOT6MB5Goj37SnmTx5UvJrh-t04W7-zHsNrfngbFbKjv58y2asHuu88AWaNjvfnVUwhVfTEO03l165YsGGUGjUPdLs_bFim-tmjDTAxQSzUMQzDvK7S8wLlG6a9H38Jh4MX7Jf7V5Nkl8Y3G9SWUkbn-OV6jGUGfvLYuSbtttYOV5uLXHPxYiN9jd1Z83hGYjpmcQR0ROB8lxG5FbV1IhavsYMCXnBQ-VLhzoEs4-ElF0Tj4LW4w0YUSpr6ykltae3f38meMjV97gisDYNLs8tNzUfufbWGqoU82aHv9v0VXOnGuhtJnnTkcKHQQ1zTBMLYaO4D8oiAEwDVxaj4mFsECkixKEZK_FUVNVGl9Qvn5Vc_2YqVsCGbhhw2K0sJj4wQGeHI8GH8GfJg8Iwuhb1vLWd12LtH-vWhFE9gDFd6B4yFuVsKa4KrPE7MLBy1TiUInbJ5T5d-3r7lLZFKAFpUqpcSlb_NR6oPQTqLzwV4svX_4q0Puctc5hUsbYZStfE8jTXKekgJG7YvzPgCcJjhN15_Pn0gZ2ylTm8FLk1pIh8uG38fXCHGrDMyKxPCR99_kxreOPRSPmwxIIIYbLdfvUn41uwd7taXhut7WjMdGTX0rDvAQCyE34f1U0lg4MA-TqhEnut5tdq9aBPszkP8qjyMvVrcZhBhfRY9xFWz4OZyDL7FcaUaq7mkq30ggyjFwreqO2fCgufPnIO2jB4IiumYZEx9Pl9NdGQsH-vE9qUaywh4mQtVaJXcNLK2kA